{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-situations-page-tsx","path":"/en/situations/shops-and-services/services","result":{"data":{"situation":{"title":"Services","meta_description":"Providing service trades is not allowed at this time.","content":{"processed":"<h2>Rules and recommendations</h2>\n<p>Providing service trades is <strong>not allowed</strong> at this time.</p>\n<p><strong>Only certain services are allowed to operate</strong>, specifically: car repair and servicing, towing services, courier services, electronics and home appliance repair and service, locksmiths, financial advisors, building and demolishing companies and saloons for cats and dogs.</p>\n<p>Any service trades not mentioned on the list of exceptions are <strong>not allowed to operate.</strong> This includes barber shops, hairdressers, manicures, pedicures, massages, cosmetic services and others. However, it is possible to have these services ordered home.</p>\n<p>If you visit a service trade, <strong>make sure to follow the hygienic rules</strong> (Hygiene section). Please, wear a mask, keep social distance and disinfect your hands.</p>\n<p>The stores can only be <strong>entered in groups of 2</strong>. The exception being children under 15 accompanied by an adult from the same household (typically parents, grandparents or siblings living with the child). <strong>Reservation of 15 square meters for one customer is mandatory</strong> for any shop or service establishments. Customers also have to keep a 2-meter distance from each other. For example in an establishment with an area of 29 square meters can be only one customer present at a time. The only exception is being accompanied by a child younger than 15 years of age. <strong>Mandatory for shops and service establishment is also the management of queues. </strong>This regulation applies to the inner area and also areas outside the establishment.</p>\n<p>Try to only use trade services when necessary and leave small repairs for another time. If you enter a shop, follow all hygienic measures, social distance and pay by card. <strong>Please, be responsible. </strong>You are protecting yourself and others.</p>\n"},"path":{"alias":"/situations/shops-and-services/services"},"changed":"2020-11-18T01:02:34+00:00","valid_from":"2020-11-04T00:00:00+01:00","langcode":"en","created":"2020-11-05T22:34:22+00:00","links":[],"relationships":{"region":[{"name":"All regions of Czechia"}],"icon":{"code":"supervisor_account"},"situation_type":{"name":"Shops and services","path":{"alias":"/situations/shops-and-services"},"relationships":{"icon":{"code":"storefront"}}},"measures":[],"related_situations":[{"title":"Indoor","path":{"alias":"/situations/face-masks/indoor","langcode":"en"}},{"title":"Shopping","path":{"alias":"/situations/shops-and-services/shopping","langcode":"en"}},{"title":"Retail","path":{"alias":"/situations/shops-and-services/retail","langcode":"en"}},{"title":"Repair shops and after-sale services","path":{"alias":"/situations/shops-and-services/repair-shops-and-after-sale-services","langcode":"en"}},{"title":"Household (shopping, repairs etc.)","path":{"alias":"/situations/household-and-housing/household-shopping-repairs-etc","langcode":"en"}},{"title":"Constructions and reconstructions","path":{"alias":"/situations/household-and-housing/constructions-and-reconstructions","langcode":"en"}},{"title":"Delivery and courier services","path":{"alias":"/situations/shops-and-services/delivery-and-courier-services","langcode":"en"}},{"title":"Measures on free movement","path":{"alias":"/situations/free-movement-people/measures-free-movement","langcode":"en"}}]},"questions_answers":[],"valid_to":null,"last_updated":"2020-11-17T23:00:00+01:00"},"situationArea":{"name":"Shops and services","path":{"alias":"/situations/shops-and-services"},"relationships":{"icon":{"code":"storefront"},"situation":[{"id":"29bf3a0d-146c-59ea-8ff1-14e061c786af","title":"Retail","path":{"alias":"/situations/shops-and-service